WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:11.000
Learn English in Los Angeles. Come to learn English in Los Angeles. We can offer you great summer English courses.

00:11.000 --> 00:20.000
You will love coming to Los Angeles to learn about American culture and improve your English at the same time.

00:20.000 --> 00:28.000
The courses last for four, six or eight weeks. They start at the end of July.

00:28.000 --> 00:38.000
Our teachers are well trained and have a lot of experience. They teach English classes for four hours a day.

00:38.000 --> 00:45.000
You can work in small or large groups. It depends on your personal choice.

00:45.000 --> 00:51.000
We provide books and we set tests every week to check your progress.

00:51.000 --> 01:03.000
There are also computers for personal study. As well as learning English, we want you to experience life in the US.

01:03.000 --> 01:10.000
You can stay as a guest with an American family and take part in their daily life.

01:10.000 --> 01:17.000
You will have meals with the family and do some activities with them too.

01:17.000 --> 01:23.000
For many of our students, this is the best part of the course.

01:23.000 --> 01:29.000
Many families form close friendships with the students and stay in touch with them.

01:29.000 --> 01:35.000
But if you prefer, of course, you can stay in a hotel.

01:35.000 --> 01:44.000
There are many exciting things to do in Los Angeles. We plan activities every day after class.

01:44.000 --> 01:53.000
You can choose to take trips to Hollywood, Disneyland or San Francisco or you can go shopping.

01:53.000 --> 02:01.000
You are certain to get the best possible experience of English learning and life in the US.

02:01.000 --> 02:06.000
You must pay for your course at least one month before it starts.

02:06.000 --> 02:13.000
Do not wait. Fill out our form and come to learn English in Los Angeles.

